# Custom Fonts
This folder contains custom font files if needed.

Recommended formats:
- WOFF2 (modern browsers)
- WOFF (fallback)
- TTF (fallback)

File naming convention:
- font-name-regular.woff2
- font-name-bold.woff2
- font-name-italic.woff2

Note: Consider using Google Fonts or system fonts for better performance.